{"tid":753841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公私合營示範: 恒基同政府交換蕉坑土地 2千平方米換9千幾","createTime":"2018-07-24T02:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T04:49:39.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ea58d06916fd7c16f086a437067008c54b769011","tid":753841,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T02:50:12.000Z","msg":"【經緯線本周提要】加快發展農地惹官商勾結疑慮<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】住得貴、住得細、住得迫，土地問題持續困擾七百幾萬香港人。各大發展商囤積逾千公頃未發展農地，政府提供配套加快農地改規劃起樓，是否解決良方？今集《經緯線》會分析發展農地的利弊，拆解香港究竟需要覓地多少？<br />\n<br />\n大埔鹿茵山莊外面有一片樹林及草地，這裏是蕉坑。<br />\n<br />\n蕉坑這幅地有三萬多平方米，分為兩區。A區靠近吐露港，有一萬四千平方米，八成半業權由政府擁有，其餘一成半由恒基地產的附屬公司及其他人持有，合共有二千平方米。在旁的B區，官地佔四成多，有九千七百平方米，另外近四成土地由恒基的附屬公司持有，其餘的一成七則屬於其他地主。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">城規會批准<ins>恒基的附屬公司</ins><ins>用A區的二千平方米土地換取B區的九千多平方米官地</ins>。換地後，A區的官地只可以興建289個公營房屋單位，恒基伙拍其他地主反而在B區可以興建506個私樓單位。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n正進行的土地供應諮詢將利用私人新界農地儲備列為選項之一，並估計各大發展商合共囤積了一千公頃未發展農地。<br />\n<br />\n規劃署前署長潘國城認為，應該成立獨立的管理局，按照發展項目對社會的貢獻加快處理這類申請。<br />\n<br />\n今個星期播出的《經緯線》會詳細分析各方對發展農地的立場，亦會探討香港要覓地多少才足夠。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=313830\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D313830&d=yNkmeMlVCs07GOpqs1huS%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=fbc57797\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D313830&h=ad30b4f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=313830</a>"},{"pid":"ea06d4c71128a982214b5ceea319998a06bbc2e4","tid":753841,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T02:50:51.000Z","msg":"本土研究社 Liber Research Community<br />\n15 hrs &middot; <br />\n【公私合營禁住搶】政府成日都強調公私合營係最佳選擇，又話絕對冇向發展商利益傾斜，咁點解社會一直都冇人信政府呢？我地唔直接答你，我地帶埋NowTV嘅經緯線記者嚟用例子答你。<br />\n<br />\n喺公私合營下，大埔蕉坑一幅地入面，恆基就成功用2000平方米嘅地，去換政府9700平方米嘅官地，然後起返500幾個私樓單位。大嗱嗱五換一嘅蝕本生意，政府都肯做，你話唔係傾斜地產商利益都冇人信啦。"},{"pid":"1695f8509548d07f05f496f38b941b3e420578d9","tid":753841,"uid":61752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T03:21:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08bf17297a68da6ab148a5384da1a46e52a1dbac","tid":753841,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T03:24:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc63a4a16ddea18b15fdefa6b3312b6b968c0afd","tid":753841,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T03:24:53.000Z","msg":"利益輸送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c344b718c3404a4a449201d983ba6af54cf4a670","tid":753841,"uid":190540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T03:25:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09f4febf2e0da6d2242a0ec172332d1e534a2af1","tid":753841,"uid":170249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T03:28:25.000Z","msg":"香港官商勾結越黎越明顯 越黎越高調<br />\n<br />\n反抗？不了 要返工<br />\n港豬們 努力返工 做奴隸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd113c898d3fccc45152052e82c8ff6f4cdbf524","tid":753841,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T03:30:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20140719/s00064/1405759885184_3DCDD09DFB032D5D8CF9820E65503790.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20140719%2Fs00064%2F1405759885184_3DCDD09DFB032D5D8CF9820E65503790.jpg&h=b5f23a96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2014年7月19日 星期六 <br />\n<br />\n恒地大埔蕉坑申建858伙<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】恒地（0012）或相關人士持有的大埔蕉坑一幅近24萬方呎地皮，近日向城規會申請由住宅（丙類）改劃為住宅（乙類）4，以將地積比率由0.6倍大升至2.1倍，擬建6幢12至22層高分層住宅，料涉約858伙。發展商亦一併將地皮以北約15萬方呎的政府地皮，申請提高地積比率，若整個規劃申請獲批，料共涉及約1394伙公私營單位。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%81%92%E5%9C%B0%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%94%E8%95%89%E5%9D%91%E7%94%B3%E5%BB%BA858%E4%BC%99/web_tc/article/20140719/s00004/1405706885386\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%2581%2592%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259F%2594%25E8%2595%2589%25E5%259D%2591%25E7%2594%25B3%25E5%25BB%25BA858%25E4%25BC%2599%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20140719%2Fs00004%2F1405706885386&d=yNkmeMlVCs07GOpqs1huS%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=bb046da4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%2581%2592%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259F%2594%25E8%2595%2589%25E5%259D%2591%25E7%2594%25B3%25E5%25BB%25BA858%25E4%25BC%2599%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20140719%2Fs00004%2F1405706885386&h=e6fdc078\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%81%92%E5%9C%B0%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%94%E8%95%89%E5%9D%91%E7%94%B3%E5%BB%BA858%E4%BC%99/web_tc/article/20140719/s00004/1405706885386</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2017年10月30日 星期一<br />\n恒地倡蕉坑2000米地換9700米官地 議員憂藉首置計劃「蛇吞象」<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】《施政報告》提出以公私營混合模式發展「港人首置上車盤」，多個發展商如恒基地產（恒地）和會德豐都率先和議。前者已成功把屬下的大埔蕉坑地與鄰近官地一併改劃用途，後者則正就擁有的洞梓地申請改劃。本報翻查城規會資料，發現改劃的蕉坑地皮，恒地建議把其擁有、分佈於公營房屋發展土地上的近2000平方米私人地，撥歸政府，以換取9000多平方米官地，讓該公司整合蕉坑地皮上的私人土地，以興建私樓，提供506個單位，另地盤則撥歸政府建289個單位。有立法會議員形容此舉為「蛇吞象」，擔心日後更多地產發展商藉首置計劃名義整合土地發展（見另稿）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20171030/s00002/1509300125827\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171030%2Fs00002%2F1509300125827&d=yNkmeMlVCs07GOpqs1huS%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=ca297d7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171030%2Fs00002%2F1509300125827&h=79c8f1ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20171030/s00002/1509300125827</a>"},{"pid":"3d4f327b57113a38a6e45a29ae6e5fb733d62eda","tid":753841,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c344b718c3404a4a449201d983ba6af54cf4a670","tid":753841,"uid":190540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T03:25:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T04:30:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能想大幅啲規劃好啲啩"},{"pid":"d5ccd431f76361b38d1103bf70e4cbc6a7303ef6","tid":753841,"uid":147226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T04:49:39.000Z","msg":"蕉土政策<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}